If you are upgrading from 0.85 to 0.90 and you want to 
use the MULTI-USER mode follow these steps.

Step 1: Download and install the Crypt::Blowfish module
from CPAN. 
(hint: su root; perl -MCPAN -e shell; install Crypt::Blowfish)

Step 2: backup your existing mysqltool.conf

Step 3: copy mysqltool.conf from the install dir to
the dir of the old mysqltool.conf

Step 4: run perl Makefile.PL; make; make install

Step 5: restart the webserver

See the pod in Mysqltool.pm for more information.
